hryge\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"her prosthetic leg\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two mascots have been given distinct personalities, with the event organisers going into considerable detail on their back stories.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The two mascots\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"distinct personalities\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"the event organisers\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"considerable detail\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1460}, {\"ngram\": \"their back stories\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Phryge is: 'Always thoughtful and an astute strategist, she embarks on adventures only after carefully weighing up all the pros and cons.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Phryge\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"adventures\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"all the pros\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"cons\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like the Olympic athletes, she knows the importance of measuring all the various parameters to achieve her goals.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"all the various parameters\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"her goals\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her sharp mind, she is modest and prefers to hide her emotions.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her sharp mind\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"her emotions\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Phryge will lead the movement of all those who take part in sport, and believe us, she will give her all to get France moving!'\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996442032873488, \"rank\": 0.0002452892257992759, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Phryge\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"the movement\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1864}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the Paralympic Phryge is described as: 'Her passion is to blaze a trail; some might say she is fearless, which might be true, but one thing is certain: she hates being bored and loves to try new things.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Phryge\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"Her passion\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"a trail\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"new things\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'No matter the sport, and regardless of whether she competes as part of a team or on her own, she is always game to play.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No matter the sport\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2247}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"game\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2291}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her, you will get moving, playing, dancing, and sweating!\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With her mindset of being the perfect supporter, she loves promoting the values of sport, celebrating athletes in all arenas and all the Games venues, and partying to celebrate victories or get over defeats.'\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2572, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mindset\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect supporter\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"the values\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2443}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"all arenas\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Games venues\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"victories\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"defeats\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mascots share the inspirational motto: 'Alone we go faster, but together we go further.'\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The mascots\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the inspirational motto\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are also said to share the message: 'Sport can change everything!\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our lives, our health, our relationships with others, how we relate to nature - it is time to welcome more sport into our lives!'\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2791}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"more sport\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2851}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was some controversy about the mascots when they were unveiled as French publicationLiberationlikened them to 'a clitoris in trainers' although this was said to be a positive thing.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2942, \"end\": 2948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6162360862426465, \"rank\": 0.4390562289492476, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some controversy\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"the mascots\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"a clitoris\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"trainers\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3009}, {\"ngram\": \"a positive thing\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'While the official mascots of the Paris Games evoke the Phrygian cap worn by Marianne, many of us saw something else there: a clitoris.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3116, \"end\": 3128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phrygian cap\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 3137, \"end\": 3145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0944304536642528e-32, \"text\": \"Marianne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the official mascots\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3105}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"a clitoris\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's good news,' wrote Quentin Girard.\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3240, \"entit